These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  designer, scientist, freelancer
The people use 3 different means of transport: tram, trike, taxi
1. the person driving the tram is not to the left of the person driving the taxi##8
2. the freelancer is somewhere to the right of the person driving the taxi##5
3. the person driving the taxi is between the scientist and the freelancer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |     3      |
| Job         | scientist | designer   | freelancer |
| Transport   | trike | taxi | tram        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, water, milk
3 different pets are kept: dog, ferret, goldfish
1. the person drinking coffee is somewhere between the person drinking milk and the owner of the dog##7
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
3. the owner of the ferret is not to the right of the person drinking coffee##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |     3      |
| Beverage   | milk | coffee   | water   |
| Pet        | ferret | goldfish | dog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-3::.
There 3 different types of food: kale, cranberry, peas
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, van, skateboard
1. the person eating kale is not to the left of the person driving the van##8
2. the person eating peas is somewhere between the person eating kale and the person driving the trike##7
3. the person eating peas is not to the left of the person driving the skateboard##8
4. the person eating peas is on the right of the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |      3      |
| Food        | cranberry | peas | kale |
| Transport   | trike       | skateboard     | van         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-4::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  teacher, mechanic, software-developer
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, fantasy, thriller
1. the software-developer is not to the right of the mechanic##8
2. the software-developer is on the right of the teacher##1
3. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere between the person watching fantasy movies and the teacher##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Job           | teacher | software-developer | mechanic |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller  | comedy | fantasy    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-5::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: drama, western, comedy
3 different pets are kept: hamster, chinchilla, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the person watching comedy movies is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
3. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching drama movies##5
4. the person watching western movies is not to the right of the person watching drama movies##8
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
6. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hamster##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3     |
| Movie-Genre   | western | comedy | drama |
| Pet           | chinchilla    | guinea-pig      | hamster  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-6::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  bartender, lawyer, nurse
3 different pets are kept: rabbit, ferret, frog
1. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the left of the bartender##5
2. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the right of the bartender##5
3. the nurse is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8
4. the lawyer is on the left of the bartender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1       |   2    |       3        |
| Job   | lawyer | bartender | nurse |
| Pet   | frog        | ferret   | rabbit     |

