.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-7::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, tea, lemonade
The people have 3 different jobs:  musician, scientist, social-worker
1. the scientist is between the social-worker and the person drinking lemonade##2
2. the person drinking tea is not to the left of the social-worker##8
3. the person drinking lemonade is not to the left of the social-worker##8
4. the social-worker is the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | milk | tea | lemonade |
| Job        | social-worker      | scientist    | musician |

