2. the person who's sport is tennis is not to the right of the person who's sport is badminton##8
3. the person who's sport is badminton is somewhere to the right of the japanese##5
4. the indonesian is not to the left of the person who's sport is badminton##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |
| Nationality   | malaysian | japanese    | indonesian |
| Sport         | cycling  | tennis | badminton |

