.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-9::.
There 3 different types of food: asparagus, artichoke, grapefruit
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: sports, spy, martial-arts
1. the person eating asparagus is somewhere to the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##5
2. the person eating grapefruit is somewhere to the left of the person eating artichoke##5
3. the person watching sports movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching spy movies is not to the right of the person eating asparagus##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |
| Food          | grapefruit | asparagus  | artichoke |
| Movie-Genre   | sports     | spy | martial-arts   |

