.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, soy-milk, iced-tea
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: swimming, rowing, badminton
1. the person drinking iced-tea is in the middle##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is not to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##8
3. the person who's sport is swimming is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is badminton##5
4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3
5. the person who's sport is rowing is somewhere to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |       2       |    3     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | iced-tea        | fanta    |
| Sport      | rowing  | badminton | swimming |

