.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-14::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, fanta, cola
The people have 3 different hobbies: video-games, writing, rock-climbing
1. the person drinking fanta is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person drinking milk##7
3. the person drinking cola is not to the right of the person drinking milk##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |     3      |
| Beverage   | fanta     | cola | milk   |
| Hobby      | rock-climbing | writing | video-games |

