.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-17::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, trance, gospel
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, weightlifting, lacrosse
1. the fan of gospel is not to the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##8
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
3. the fan of gospel is between the fan of trance and the fan of ambient##2
4. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the fan of trance is not to the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |
| Music-Genre   | ambient       | gospel      | trance |
| Sport         | rowing | weightlifting | lacrosse     |

