2. the owner of the goldfish is not to the right of the owner of the goldfish##8
3. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the person eating nectarine##5
4. the person eating kale is on the left or right of the person eating nectarine##3
5. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the owner of the snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |     2     |     3      |
| Food   | pumpkin | nectarine | kale    |
| Pet    | goldfish   | horse      | snake |

