3. the person watching sports movies is somewhere between the person watching horror movies and the person watching satire movies##7
4. the person watching satire movies is not to the left of the egyptian##8
5. the egyptian is not to the left of the person watching sports movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |
| Movie-Genre   | horror   | sports    | satire  |
| Nationality   | dutch | french | egyptian |

