.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-20::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: skydiving, sudoku, rock-climbing
There are 3 different nationalities: thai, colombian, pakistani
1. the colombian is somewhere between the pakistani and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##7
2. the thai is not to the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##8
3. the thai is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |      3      |
| Hobby         | skydiving | sudoku | rock-climbing |
| Nationality   | pakistani  | colombian    | thai    |

 